Wordpress theme folder is located in wp-content/themes folder
    -> create new theme by creating a new folder
    -> inside the folder add index.php and style.css
    -> style.css is the needed name of the css file
    -> Start with creating a comment
        -> Inside the comment is the Theme Name: your choice of theme name, Author, and Version
    -> Name the theme thumbnail screenshot.png

<?php bloginfo() -> wordpress built-in function?>